{"tid":2258094,"cid":5,"subCid":12,"title":"乜撚野612，攬炒巴，光時仲衰過d美容雞金融雞","createTime":"2020-10-25T17:35:43.000Z","updateTime":"2020-10-26T13:42:40.000Z","uid":93277,"like":30,"dislike":50,"uniUserReply":8,"replies":[{"pid":"58d406cd881768680578b40db8dd1c52b72a2c98","tid":2258094,"uid":93277,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-10-25T17:35:43.000Z","msg":"人地美容雞金融雞都叫憑實力或者比人抽水黎搵錢，<br />\n<br />\n屌你老母乜撚野612，攬炒巴，光時全部淨係識叫人捐錢捐錢，光時就比人篤爆出十皮野一個月，<br />\n<br />\n乜撚野612，攬炒巴你夠唔撚夠膽講你出緊幾錢一個月糧呀屌你老母<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/clown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />班義士就坐監無淡好食，你班撚樣係外國好食好住<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/clown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"af60c2e11c7252aa6447d52b096e517a5bcc6dda","tid":2258094,"uid":6003,"like":1,"dislike":1,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-10-25T17:36:32.000Z","msg":"連登五毛/五毛幫兇 每日task list<br />\n<a href=\"https://lih.kg/2225999\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">https://lih.kg/2225999</a><br />\n- 分享自 LIHKG 討論區"},{"pid":"8ead0f2307ee5585cf2f0e80a886795592bcdda3","tid":2258094,"uid":171506,"like":3,"dislike":2,"score":1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-10-25T17:37:30.000Z","msg":"blocked"},{"pid":"092590a0a09b1339695ce395a36718379d757cda","tid":2258094,"uid":6003,"like":4,"dislike":1,"score":3,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-10-25T17:38:52.000Z","msg":"終於記得點解追蹤左呢個人<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n<br />\n又遺言又遺書，一開槍咪又係走鳩晒<br />\n<a href=\"https://lih.kg/1731887\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">https://lih.kg/1731887</a><br />\n- 分享自 LIHKG 討論區"},{"pid":"8eef1794a2af035c4eb8b6d3f0540eea7d26e9ff","tid":2258094,"uid":93277,"like":5,"dislike":6,"score":-1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-10-25T17:38:54.000Z","msg":"駁唔撚到就淨係識5毛，分化，block，叫佢班撚樣出黎講出緊幾錢一個月糧啦<img src=\"/assets/faces/lm2/brain.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"57385041cefcafab62476c2dd4d681ff81b4d984","tid":2258094,"uid":6003,"like":2,"dislike":1,"score":1,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2020-10-25T17:39:45.000Z","msg":"呢個post又係<img src=\"/